description:
Watch Holy Moly Volume 2 on Vision Video

Episode 1: Rebekah and Isaac
Episode 2: Jacob and Esau
Episode 3: Jacob Becomes Israel  
Episode 4: Joseph and His Brothers 
Episode 5: Joseph Interprets Pharaohs Dream
Episode 6: Joseph Forgives

Holy Moly turns the Bible into a living, breathing coloring book that will delight children of all ages.  Eyes will be fixed on the screen, observing how God is at work in the story when color is introduced to an otherwise black-and-white world.  Rather than dialogue, the series focuses on the Biblical characters actions and emotions to help audiences of any language or background immediately relate to and remember these enriching stories.

Holy Moly captivates children with imaginative retellings of classic Bible stories, where every splash of color helps kids discover how God is at work.

Directors: Jared Neher, Aaron Christopher
Writers: Aaron Christopher, Nick Ryan
Producers: Jared Neher, Aaron Christopher
Cast: Debra Thorpe Hetherington, Svea Rundman, Troy Zimmerman
